BCD Configurations
==================

This directory may contain Bonita Continuous Delivery (BCD) configurations
used to build and deploy this repository artifacts on different environments
(eg. Development, Test, Staging, Production).

Configuration files in this directory are encrypted with Ansible Vault.
Then you may set your environment for Ansible Vault as follows:

    `ANSIBLE_VAULT_PASSWORD_FILE=/path/to/.bcd_vault_password.txt`

(adapt the above path accordingly)


WARNING! This example repository contains a `.bcd_vault_password.txt` file
         **for demo purposes only**. You must NOT store this file in your
         repository during normal operations.

